data.description: Enjoy the stunning golf course across the street and Organ mountain views with this spectacular Sonoma Golf Community Southwestern-style home sitting on a .23 acre corner lot with 2,104 sq ft of living space featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a utility/laundry room with cupboards and counter space, and an oversized 2 car garage with storage shelves. Interior features large living area windows with views of the mountains, a beautiful fireplace, skylights throughout, and even includes a Kinetico water softener. Master bathroom has a deep jetted tub, separate shower stall, double sink with tile countertop. The kitchen features gorgeous granite countertops, custom wood cabinetry and a large island with wine storage. Exterior features a professionally landscaped yard, circular driveway, 2 HVAC units, a covered patio area, and a custom matched gazebo with tile rooftop with a hot tub outlet at reach!
